<article class="module column product"><h1>Gold Range Replicator </h1><img src="images/content/replicator.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Dutch Master</dd><dt>Available in</dt><dd>60 ml</dd></dl><p>Gold Range REPLICATOR is a new, naturally formed, gentle cutting gel that gives you great success time and time again when taking cuttings. Gold Range REPLICATOR is a new and specialized cut stem sealant, designed and reformulated by our in-house Plant Sciences team, that nurtures your newly taken cutting in a revolutionary and nutritious cocoon. This cocoon ensures trouble free and successful rooting by providing a specialized environment - bathing the cut end of the stem in a nutritious bath of selected British &amp; US Pharmaceutical grade mineral elements and photo-nutrients. Your cuttings are encouraged to produce roots naturally, not artificially with harsh hormones.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Flower Seed Soak </h1><img src="images/content/flowerseedsoak.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Accent Solutions</dd><dt>Available in</dt><dd>50ml</dd></dl><p>Flower Seed Soak stimulates the seed, to encourage a tendency for the plant to become female. This results in more flowering sites and an overall greater flower development.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Seed and Clone </h1><img src="images/content/seednclone.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Accent Solutions</dd><dt>Available in</dt><dd>500ml, 1L</dd></dl><p>Seed'n'Clone starter solution is and advanced formulation designed specifically for germinating seeds and cuttings and contains all the necessary elements needed for accelerated root development.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Jiffy Pots</h1><img src="images/content/jiffys.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Available in</dt><dd>Pack of 24</dd></dl><p>The easiest way to grow your seeds.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Propogation Box Large</h1><img src="images/content/propogationbox.jpg" alt=""><p>Used to raise seedlings and cuttings.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Clonex Cloning Solution </h1><img src="images/content/clonexsolution.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Growth Technology</dd><dt>Available in</dt><dd>250ml, 500ml, 1L, 5.5L, 20L</dd></dl><p>CCS is a super-concentrated nutrient formula containing a special blend of minerals, vitamins, wetting agents and root promoters.  Clonex Cloning Solution encourages rapid and profuse root development and guards against the inevitable stress associated with stock transplants.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>390x400 Heat Pad with thermostat</h1><img src="images/content/heatpad.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Thermofilm</dd></dl><p>For most species, the ideal rooting temperature is around 23DegC to 28DegC. Heat is best supplied from underneath (bottom heat) to encourage root cell initiation. It is most important that temperature remains constant. Best way to provide bottom heat is by use of a heated propagator or heat mat.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Gold Range A.P.S. </h1><img src="images/content/goldaps.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Dutch Master</dd><dt>Available in</dt><dd>1L, 5L</dd></dl><p>Gold Range A.P.S perfectly conditions Rockwool cubes and slabs to successfully accept cuttings and as Gold Range A.P.S is ready to use straight out of the bottle (no dilution required), using it is a snap! Use as foliar spray also.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>390x400 Heat Pad with no thermostat</h1><img src="images/content/heatpad.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Thermofilm</dd></dl><p>For most species, the ideal rooting temperature is around 23DegC to 28DegC. Heat is best supplied from underneath (bottom heat) to encourage root cell initiation. It is most important that temperature remains constant. Best way to provide bottom heat is by use of a heated propagator or heat mat.</p></article>